Title: Step 7: Return to Marcus Eldridge
Text: Now that I’ve handed over the White Stag to the taxidermist, it’s time to return to Marcus Eldridge and update him on my progress.
CompleteText: I’ve returned to Marcus Eldridge to review my progress. The taxidermist will send me the mounted White Stag once it's ready. I’m now ready to move on to the next chapter.
